These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
House: craftsman, townhouse, gothic-revival
1. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| House   | townhouse | gothic-revival | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, romance
1. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | fantasy | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | july | april | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, dannemann
1. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar   | montecristo | dannemann | cain |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, whist
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Game   | backgammon | scrabble | whist |

 #################################

 
