.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-8::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goat, dog
1. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |    3    |
| Pet   | goat | dog | ferret |

